  "instructions": [
    "Heat sesame oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add garlic and ginger and stir-fry for 1 minute, until fragrant.",
    "Add squid tubes and stir-fry for 2-3 minutes, until they start to change color.",
    "Add fermented bean paste, salt, and black pepper. Stir-fry for another minute.",
    "Pour in coconut milk and stir-fry for 2-3 minutes, until the sauce thickens.",
    "Stir in white chocolate chips until melted and creamy.",
    "Garnish with green onions and serve hot."
